stimulusHtml: What, if anything, is printed as a result of executing the code segment?

features.html:
In the following code segment, assume that the  ArrayList  object  numbers  has been properly declared and initialized to contain  [0, 2, 4, 5].

 

for (int k = numbers.size() - 1; k >= 0; k--) 
{ 
   if (numbers.get(k) > k) 
   { 
      System.out.print(k + " "); 
   } 
}

choicesHtml: Nothing is printed because an  IndexOutOfBoundsException  is thrown.
